5%25a5%25e4%25be%25b5&h=61444e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190829/s00001/1567081744488/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e7%b6%b2%e5%82%b3%e9%96%a9%e5%83%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%ad%b8%e5%89%af%e6%a0%a1fb%e8%b2%bc%e3%80%8c%e6%8b%92%e6%9b%b1%e7%94%b4%e8%ab%96%e3%80%8d-%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9-%e5%a5%b9%e5%b8%b3%e6%88%b6%e8%a2%ab%e5%85%a5%e4%be%b5</a><br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》風波不斷。今日網上流傳一張聲稱是北角閩僑中學宋副校長的facebook帖文截圖，內容為「我唔歡迎啲死曱甴做我哋學校嘅學生」。校長羅惠金回覆本報查詢時稱，得知網上流傳有關帖文截圖，她即時向宋副校長查證，確定宋副校長沒有發出有關帖文，「明顯地她facebook帳戶被人入侵，因此要立即停用」，而帖文由來需待調查。<br />\n<br />\n羅惠金稱，已認識宋副校長多年，相信她行為操守，確定她不會說出此等言論。她稱，未能確認宋副校長的facebook帳戶被人入侵，或是有人偽造該圖，需待跟進。她說，在目前政治風波下，學校或被牽連，憂慮學校被針對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190829/s00001/a56aa9a1f2423ae33ef2acc078d8f302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190829%2Fs00001%2Fa56aa9a1f2423ae33ef2acc078d8f302.jpg&h=cd659300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有野都係比人hack</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6ac3b40f17debc2b93d149002e8e43c18db24ac5","tid":1516250,"uid":25048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"淋病都可以不代表政府啦"},{"pid":"501e320ae66aed4cbc02e85b510a8454bcf7b3b3","tid":1516250,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"CX員工都係比人HACK<br />\n復職先講"},{"pid":"097233b98d97e39730f1a8dd35b19484c1786e03","tid":1516250,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"問下黑警學校比人欺凌要點話"},{"pid":"6debbc4f18afb733b753256d2810233deef9432e","tid":1516250,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9368c1f5bbb47c58d3c71d5efb44f2ee0e6a88","tid":1516250,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep